{"tid":2367840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭偉強往中區警署自首 暫無被檢控","createTime":"2021-01-15T16:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T17:32:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa119c1d344891232284a81d23b159bfa43429b4","tid":2367840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"工聯會郭偉強昨天（14日）於立法會房屋事務委員會以Zoom開會期間，被人發現他疑似一邊揸車、一邊開會，涉嫌違反《道路交通條例》，不小心駕駛，但他昨天堅稱不覺自己犯法，又嬉皮笑臉式回應「車上暖氣是我的避寒中心」，稱左撲右撲都是為社區服務。公職人員涉違法，事關重大，郭偉強今天在3位黨友陪同下見記者，就事件公開致歉，聲言會深刻反省駕駛態度；他避談會否自首，只稱有需要時會配合調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，一名42歲男子主動就一宗交通事件聯絡警方，並於今晚獲安排到中區警署與警方會面，案件由港島總區交通部跟進調查，暫未有人被檢控，惟警方未有回應是否接獲市民就相關事件的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/4JF4RLIXIVE7LJRVMAVQSRLLCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2F4JF4RLIXIVE7LJRVMAVQSRLLCY%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7fa8ac98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2F4JF4RLIXIVE7LJRVMAVQSRLLCY%2F&h=daecd20e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/4JF4RLIXIVE7LJRVMAVQSRLLCY/</a>"},{"pid":"f0bfa251ff478487bdc1364592c3a06d28f508d2","tid":2367840,"uid":76804,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"又無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我都心郁郁想做藍絲添<br />\n撞斷腳 醉駕 打人 渣住車開會都無事咁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d0b659ba6fd9c1cc62dd2ef0c2a5896fab0bf3","tid":2367840,"uid":151313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T16:11:00.000Z","msg":"傷人都冇事啦"},{"pid":"8c951ef85b873a37c7020a836b5266c572810064","tid":2367840,"uid":605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T16:12:03.000Z","msg":"佢jm9"},{"pid":"3e1282b2ee6d36342916dc1946f5